      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VOLTS (6) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (23.08) at this track behind Ziva Diva in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Can measure up this time. STAR OF VENUS (8) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (22.78) in a Grade 5 at Shepparton. Solid record here winning eight races. Cannot be underestimated. PRINCESS DOMI (1) recorded her best time this course and distance latest, finishing a 4 length third behind Berringa Paddy in 22.94. Strong run and expected to feature again. COMEBACK CHARLIE (7) is right in the mix.",
